<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻 |路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - 由 RSSHub 提供支持</description><lastBuildDate>Mon, 13 Jan 2025 18:21:01 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>墨西哥的谢因鲍姆制定了使该国成为经济强国的路线图</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/americas/mexicos-sheinbaum-lays-out-roadmap-make-country-an-economic-powerhouse-2025-01-13/</link><description>墨西哥总统克劳迪娅·辛鲍姆周一推出了她的政府路线图，以期在她离任时使该国成为世界顶级经济体之一。</description><pubDate>Mon, 13 Jan 2025 17:53:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/americas/mexicos-sheinbaum-lays-out-roadmap-make-country-an-economic-powerhouse-2025-01-13/</guid></item><item><title>IDC称，由于中国竞争加剧，苹果、三星智能手机出货量第四季度下降</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/apple-samsung-smartphone-shipments-fall-fourth-quarter-china-competition-bites-2025-01-13/</link><description>国际数据公司（IDC）周一公布的初步数据显示，苹果和三星在应对来自小米等中国公司的激烈竞争时，第四季度全球智能手机出货量出现下降。</description><pubDate>Mon, 13 Jan 2025 17:41:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/apple-samsung-smartphone-shipments-fall-fourth-quarter-china-competition-bites-2025-01-13/</guid></item><item><title>碧桂园物业服务部门预计全年盈利将下降</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/country-gardens-property-services-arm-expects-annual-earnings-fall-2025-01-13/</link><description>中国建筑商碧桂园旗下的物业服务部门预计，其环卫业务计划计提商誉和有形资产减值准备，其年收益将最多下降11亿元人民币（1.5003亿美元）。</description><pubDate>Mon, 13 Jan 2025 16:11:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/country-gardens-property-services-arm-expects-annual-earnings-fall-2025-01-13/</guid></item><item><title>Wizz Air 首席执行官预计普惠发动机问题将持续 4-5 年</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/aerospace-defense/wizz-air-ceo-sees-pratt-whitney-engine-woes-lasting-4-5-years-2025-01-13/</link><description>这家低成本航空公司首席执行官周一表示，普惠公司 RTX 发动机的问题导致维兹航空部分飞机停飞，该问题可能会持续四到五年。</description><pubDate>Mon, 13 Jan 2025 15:29:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/aerospace-defense/wizz-air-ceo-sees-pratt-whitney-engine-woes-lasting-4-5-years-2025-01-13/</guid></item><item><title>美国最高法院驳回石油公司驳回檀香山气候诉讼的请求</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sustainability/climate-energy/us-supreme-court-rejects-bid-by-oil-companiesshell-toss-honolulus-climate-suit-2025-01-13/</link><description>美国最高法院周一拒绝听取太阳石油公司和其他石油公司驳回檀香山提起的诉讼的请求，该诉讼指控这些公司数十年来在燃烧化石燃料引起的气候变化危险方面误导公众。</description><pubDate>Mon, 13 Jan 2025 14:45:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sustainability/climate-energy/us-supreme-court-rejects-bid-by-oil-companiesshell-toss-honolulus-climate-suit-2025-01-13/</guid></item><item><title>消息人士称，中国电池巨头宁德时代聘请银行进行上半年香港上市</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/chinas-battery-giant-catl-hires-banks-first-half-hong-kong-float-sources-say-2025-01-13/</link><description>两位知情人士表示，中国电池巨头宁德时代已聘请摩根大通和美国银行等银行参与香港上市事宜，这可能是该市 2025 年最大规模的上市之一。</description><pubDate>Mon, 13 Jan 2025 13:52:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/chinas-battery-giant-catl-hires-banks-first-half-hong-kong-float-sources-say-2025-01-13/</guid></item><item><title>出租人SMBC Aviation首席执行官表示几乎所有飞机都被延误</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/aerospace-defense/ceo-lessor-smbc-aviation-says-almost-every-aircraft-being-delayed-2025-01-13/</link><description>飞机租赁巨头SMBC Aviation Capital的负责人周一表示，波音和空客交付的几乎每架飞机都被推迟，随后又补充说，发动机制造商在解决问题方面已做出了轻微改进。</description><pubDate>Mon, 13 Jan 2025 13:42:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/aerospace-defense/ceo-lessor-smbc-aviation-says-almost-every-aircraft-being-delayed-2025-01-13/</guid></item><item><title>西藏上周地震后发生两次强烈余震</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/environment/earthquakes-hit-tibets-tingri-county-2025-01-13/</link><description>中国西藏地区的一个农村县仍感受到上周 6.8 级地震的震感，周一晚上又发生了两次相隔不到一分钟的强烈余震。</description><pubDate>Mon, 13 Jan 2025 13:22:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/environment/earthquakes-hit-tibets-tingri-county-2025-01-13/</guid></item><item><title>OpenAI 敦促美国优先考虑人工智能资金和监管，以保持领先于中国</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/artificial-intelligence/openai-urges-us-prioritize-ai-funding-regulation-stay-ahead-china-2025-01-13/</link><description>OpenAI 周一阐述了美国人工智能发展的愿景，称美国需要外部投资和支持性监管，才能在新兴技术的竞争中保持领先于中国。</description><pubDate>Mon, 13 Jan 2025 13:07:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/artificial-intelligence/openai-urges-us-prioritize-ai-funding-regulation-stay-ahead-china-2025-01-13/</guid></item><item><title>中国誓言扩大单边免签国家名单</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-vows-expand-list-unilateral-visa-free-countries-2025-01-13/</link><description>中国政府周一发布的措施显示，中国将扩大单边免签国家名单并延长免签停留期限。</description><pubDate>Mon, 13 Jan 2025 11:47:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-vows-expand-list-unilateral-visa-free-countries-2025-01-13/</guid></item><item><title>中国恒大旗下子公司收到香港法院的清算令</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-evergrandes-unit-receives-liquidation-order-hong-kong-court-2025-01-13/</link><description>中国恒大周一表示，香港一家法院已下令将其一个主要离岸子公司清盘，这是这家陷入困境的开发商清算人取得的一系列法律胜利中的最新一起。</description><pubDate>Mon, 13 Jan 2025 11:26:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-evergrandes-unit-receives-liquidation-order-hong-kong-court-2025-01-13/</guid></item><item><title>早盘竞价：因债券困扰，标普 500 指数抹去了大选后的涨幅</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-2025-01-13/</link><description>迈克·多兰 (Mike Dolan) 对美国和全球市场未来一天的展望</description><pubDate>Mon, 13 Jan 2025 11:17:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-2025-01-13/</guid></item><item><title>德国高端汽车制造商在中国和德国的销售因经济放缓而遭受重创</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/bmw-group-annual-sales-fall-weak-demand-china-germany-2025-01-13/</link><description>销量数据显示，2024 年德国高端汽车制造商在国内和中国都遭受重创，因为经济不确定且电动汽车销售低于预期，较富裕的消费者抑制了购买。</description><pubDate>Mon, 13 Jan 2025 11:10:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/bmw-group-annual-sales-fall-weak-demand-china-germany-2025-01-13/</guid></item><item><title>美国新的人工智能芯片规则将如何运作</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/artificial-intelligence/how-new-ai-chip-rule-us-will-work-2025-01-13/</link><description>该规则规范了最复杂的人工智能应用所需的美国人工智能芯片和技术的流动。</description><pubDate>Mon, 13 Jan 2025 11:04:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/artificial-intelligence/how-new-ai-chip-rule-us-will-work-2025-01-13/</guid></item><item><title>美国收紧对全球人工智能芯片流动的控制</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/artificial-intelligence/us-tightens-its-grip-ai-chip-flows-across-globe-2025-01-13/</link><description>美国政府周一表示，将进一步限制人工智能芯片和技术出口，瓜分全球，将先进计算能力保留在美国及其盟友手中，同时寻找更多方式阻止中国进入。</description><pubDate>Mon, 13 Jan 2025 11:03:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/artificial-intelligence/us-tightens-its-grip-ai-chip-flows-across-globe-2025-01-13/</guid></item></channel></rss>